			dependencies: ["6724AAFC3D535090"]
			description: ["Forests supply the bulk of your early wood. Oak provides the widest material compatibility for vanilla and modded recipes alike. Canopy density means forest mobs are more dangerous at night — build or seek shelter before dark."]
