		{
			dependencies: ["A001000000000001"]
			description: ["Dark Forests are dense enough to block direct sunlight — monsters spawn even at midday beneath the canopy. The Woodland Mansion, home to the Evoker and its Vex minions, generates only in this biome. The Totem of Undying the Evoker drops is one of the most valuable items in the early-to-mid game."]
