		{
			dependencies: ["6724AAFC3D535090"]
			description: ["Jungles are the densest biome in the game — cocoa beans, melons, and parrots are found here exclusively. Jungle temples contain loot behind tripwire puzzles; disarm them before looting. Ocelots spawn naturally and can be tamed with raw fish. The density of foliage makes navigation difficult but rewarding."]
