		{
			dependencies: ["A001000000000005"]
			description: ["Badlands (Mesa) are one of the rarest overworld biomes — gold ore generates at all Y levels here, far above its normal range. Mineshafts expose at the surface as oxidized wood structures cutting through the red and orange terracotta layers. A reliable early gold source with spectacular visual character."]
