		{
			dependencies: ["6724AAFC3D535090"]
			description: ["Taiga biomes host spruce trees and wolves. Wolves are tameable with bones and become loyal companions with full health tracking. Berry bushes damage without protection. Pillager outposts and villages generate here. The snow variant houses Strays — undead archers that fire slowness-tipped arrows. Sweet Berries are an early food source here."]
