			dependencies: ["A001000000000008"]
			description: ["The Frozen Peaks are among the highest-elevation biomes — jagged, snow-covered mountain summits where only Goats and the occasional powder snow trap await. Goats ram players and mobs off ledges; a Screaming Goat's horn is a rare drop with utility uses. The peak elevation makes them natural landmarks."]
