		{
			dependencies: ["A001000000000011"]
			description: ["The Mushroom Fields biome is one of the safest in the game — hostile mobs do not spawn here naturally. Giant Mycelium mushrooms and Mooshrooms define the landscape. Mooshrooms can be milked for Mushroom Stew, a renewable infinite food source. The biome is rare and typically generates on isolated ocean islands."]
