			dependencies: ["6724AAFC3D535090"]
			description: ["The Soul Sand Valley is a distinctive Nether biome — blue fire burns on soul sand, Ghasts float through open caverns, and skeletons congregate in dense numbers. Soul Sand slows movement; Soul Soil does not. Soul Speed enchantment grants movement bonus. The aesthetic is used heavily in Soul Land cultivation themes."]
