		{
			dependencies: ["6724AAFC3D535090"]
			description: ["The Warped Forest is the only Nether biome where Endermen spawn naturally. It is otherwise peaceful — no hostile Nether mobs spawn here. Warped Fungi drives away Hoglins. The blue-cyan palette contrasts the rest of the Nether sharply. Endermen from this biome carry ender pearls useful for early teleportation and Ender Chest crafting."]
