			dependencies: ["6724AAFC3D535090"]
			description: ["Basalt Deltas are harsh even by Nether standards — Magma Cubes spawn in swarms, the terrain is uneven black basalt and magma blocks, and visibility is low. Basalt itself is a useful stone-type building material with a distinctive volcanic look. Ghasts float above the delta valleys."]
