		{
			dependencies: ["6724AAFC3D535090"]
			description: ["The Undergarden is an underground dimension of permanent twilight — bioluminescent fungi and crystal formations fill caverns beneath the surface. Stalactite clusters drip with exotic fluids. Unique ores (Cloggrum, Froststeel, Utherium) are found only here. Use a portal frame with Warpstone to enter. The Undergarden connects naturally to the cave system below your world."]
