			dependencies: ["6724AAFC3D535090"]
			description: ["The Aether is a sky dimension of floating islands, eternal daylight, and dangerous dungeons filled with unique bosses. Enter through a water-activated portal. The Aether contains materials unavailable elsewhere — Zanite for tools, Gravitite for armor that falls upward, and the Aether dungeons for rare accessories. The Slider, Valkyrie Queen, and Sun Spirit guard the tier-locked loot."]
