			dependencies: ["6724AAFC3D535090"]
			description: ["Alex's Caves are not a separate dimension — they are underground biome variants that replace standard caves at deep elevations. Magnetic Caves contain floating ore deposits and unique magnetic mobs. Toxic Caves are filled with poisonous gas. Crystal Caves grow enormous gemstone formations. Each variant requires preparation before entry; do not descend unprepared."]
